When a channel is enabled back, the lenght counters remains zero until some new value is written to $4003/$4007/$400b/$400f. The only change is that they're not forced to zero any longer.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Thu Oct 29, 2009 10:04 am</p><hr />
